1. filtering  
?category=smartphones
?category=smartphones&discount.type=shipping

2.sorting
?_sort=price&_order=desc //boyukden kichiye
?_sort=price&_order=asc //kichiden boyuye

?_sort=category  //category gore sorting, elifba sirasina gore

3.pagination
?_page=1  ilk 10 dene gelir
?_page=1&_limit=2 

4.
?price_gte=1&price_lte=100(1 ve 100 arasindakilari getir)

5.
?id_ne=1 (id-si 1 olandan bashqalarini getir)
?category_like=^s (s herifi ile bashlaynalari)
?q=kl(hardaki sozlerin arasinds kl var)

6. relation
?_embed=categories (categories ile birge datalari getir)
/1?_embed=categories (1ci-nin categories ile birge getir)
/categories?_expand=product (categories(1) ona uygun olan product(2)ile birge getirir)
/categories/4?_expand=product